===文化致因===
欧洲历史上童工盛行，在现代社会童工也依然存在，一些文化认可童工，并对其进行鼓励。有的认为劳动对塑造儿童品质和技巧有利。在许多文化裡，特别是非正式经济单位和小型家庭作坊里童工泛滥，其文化传统是子继父业；童工即是在早年就学习并实践劳动。类似地，在一些文化里，重男轻女也很流行，女孩得不到教育，被排除在正式教育之外，进入童工行列，如家仆等。<ref name=ilo2008a/><ref>{{cite web|title=CHILD LABOUR: ISSUES, CAUSES AND INTERVENTIONS|author=Faraaz Siddiqi and Harry Anthony Patrinos |publisher=The World Bank|year=1999|url=http://siteresources.worldbank.org/EDUCATION/Resources/278200-1099079877269/547664-1099079934475/547667-1135281552767/Child_Labour_issues.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Exploring the causes of child labour|author=Obinna E. Osita-Oleribe|journal=International NGO Journal|volume=2|issue=1|pages=6–9|date=January 2007|url=http://www.academicjournals.org/ingoj/pdf/Pdf2007/Jan/Osita-Oleribe.pdf|access-date=2015-05-16|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609045119/https://academicjournals.org/ingoj/pdf/Pdf2007/Jan/Osita-Oleribe.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Child Labour in Latin America: Poverty as Cause and Effect|author=Michaelle Tauson|year=2009|url=http://www.du.edu/korbel/hrhw/researchdigest/latinamerica2/digest-human%20rights%20in%20latin%20america%20vol%202-childlabour.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Child Labour and Cultural Relativism: From 19th Century America to 21st Century Nepal|author=Michele D'Avolio|journal=Pace International Law Review|date=Spring 2004|volume=16|issue=1|url=http://digitalcommons.pace.edu/pilr/vol16/iss1/5/|access-date=2015-05-16|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225125350/https://digitalcommons.pace.edu/pilr/vol16/iss1/5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

